{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18side", "eventName": "塵影餘音", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "LE-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "月光", "storyInfo": "芙蓉得知了夕照區的一些過往；黑鍵正要抓人，女皇的密探卻突然現身，傳謠之人趁機逃入下水道，兩人尾隨追上。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g3_slumstreets_night", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_488_1$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說了別回頭，人被你放跑了吧。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是誰？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯爵大人，冷靜，冷靜。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正式的身份解釋起來有點麻煩，你就當我是一名密探吧。我叫別格勒。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......為什麼要挑這個時候跳出來？人是被你放跑的！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正是跑進了下水道裡，他要想從別的出入口逃出去，要花好長時間。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，你在他進去之前就把他叫住，誰知道是不是你們察覺到了什麼，見勢不妙，想跟我演戲呢。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想跟你演戲？我和他？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，你之前去找格特魯德其實是被脅迫的？可別逗了。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的價值比他高多了，烏提卡伯爵。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你攔不住我。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "論打架，我確實攔不住你，但你可要想好。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是女皇陛下頒發的委任狀，你可以看看。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這玩意兒我六歲就有了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬥嘴我沒意見，不過事關女皇陛下，你最好收斂點。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收斂？倒是你，區區一個密探，等你明白自己抓錯了人，你才是吃不了兜著走的那個。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對自己的處境似乎還沒什麼自覺，親愛的烏提卡伯爵。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，別在這拖延時間了，跟我走吧。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去哪？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去你該去的地方。別擔心，我們為各個階層的嫌疑犯準備了符合他們身份的拘押處，你算最高級的那一批。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，別格勒先生。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "準備求饒了？還是賄賂？如果是後者，我很樂意收下。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很懷疑，如果我給你錢，你真的會放我走嗎？我怎麼覺得你把錢收進口袋之後，還是會把我抓走呢？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聰明。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我開始覺得和你相處很讓人痛快了，別格勒先生。你讓我想起我熟悉的烏提卡，那裡的人大多和你一樣“高尚”。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "榮幸之至。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我真的很想知道，剛才那個人要在下水道裡搞什麼名堂。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你在我的眼皮子底下把他叫住了。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個嘛，說來慚愧，我想在地面上解決這件事。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的某位伯爵代理喜歡搜集讓人倒胃口的故事。在一系列讓人吃不下飯的故事裡，只有下水道的故事勁頭最大。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，既然覺得倒胃口，不如去喝杯咖啡緩一緩。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想走，可我還是想知道他到底想做什麼，只好也跟著他鑽進去了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可都是你害的啊，別格勒先生。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你放我進去，大可以一直用法杖對準我，我不會跑的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我事先警告你，擅自脫離我的控制，不管出於什麼原因，都一定會受到懲罰。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會怎麼樣？死刑？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少也是降爵。你以後一步也不能踏進烏提卡的高塔，就算你真的清白無辜也不行。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那真是太好了，我甚至有點想試著跑一跑了呢。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，既然你非要進去不可，那就請進吧，烏提卡伯爵。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會緊緊盯著你的。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蓉啊，不是要說你，你不能那麼跟先生說話啊。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是車爾尼先生他......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有很多話，先生自己是說不出口的，只好由老婆子我來說了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您請講。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道夕照區的名字是怎麼來的嗎？", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生以前說過一句話。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說：“正因為天要黑了，夕照才更顯可貴。如果長夜永無盡頭，還有什麼比帶著暖意的餘暉更奪目、更能打動人心呢？”", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這句話說得確實很好，但是......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，那邊兩位——烏爾蘇拉大姐，還有芙蓉？", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來來來，有什麼話在這坐著聊！", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蓉還是皺著眉頭啊，出什麼事了？", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#3$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是怕我做的東西不健康，我這還有氣泡水，來吧，來吧！", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還是——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們就恭敬不如從命啦。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏爾蘇拉大姐，芙蓉怎麼啦，和誰吵架了？", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是吵架，別瞎說。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是想給芙蓉講一講夕照區的舊事。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕照區的舊事？這個我可太熟了。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是我吹牛，烏爾蘇拉大姐都沒我知道得多。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這夕照區，原本可不是什麼感染者聚居區，而是維謝海姆的工業地塊之一。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你別看我現在在這擺攤，當年也管著好幾百號人的伙食呢。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工業......難道說，這裡之所以會變成感染者聚居區，是因為工業污染導致的礦石病傳播？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工業確實帶來了許多感染者，但以前的萊塔尼亞，是沒有感染者聚居區這種東西的......哎，我就不瞎說了。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一年，那位陛下一聲令下，維謝海姆建起了一座驚世駭俗的音樂廳......就是現在的夕照廳了。當時音樂廳也不叫這個名字。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位陛下......哪位陛下？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎喲，芙蓉，這種事我們還是意會吧，好不好？", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然說是“那位”......", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "音樂廳剛落成時，那位陛下還在位，誰也不敢說什麼。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可那位陛下很快就不在了，接手維謝海姆的斯特羅洛伯爵很討厭這座音樂廳。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能不是討厭，而是......急著表忠心吧。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓——可別瞎說。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#3$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過了幾年，上面下了令，說是要提高感染者的待遇，當時的伯爵就順勢把音樂廳連同工業地塊，一同劃成了感染者聚居區。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之前，找遍整個萊塔尼亞，也沒有“感染者聚居區”這種東西。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時的伯爵......不是現在這位格特魯德女士？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是她的父親——還是兄長來著......我記不清了，反正不是她本人。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時的伯爵大人雖然把這個區塊劃成了感染者聚居區，卻完全不管我們這些人的死活，甚至把地塊上的工業設施都拆走了......", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明擺著就是要放我們自生自滅。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是在那些貴族口中，我們這兒就成了“夕照區”，那座音樂廳就成了“夕照廳”。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所謂“夕照”，就是說我們這些人像傍晚的太陽一樣，沒多長時間了。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這——這實在太惡毒了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實挺過分的。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對當時的夕照區來說，這個詞也算貼切。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家拼了命地活下去，讓太陽能再在地平線上掙扎一段時間。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擺攤，跑腿，甚至給其他地塊的有錢人當打手......唉，那幾年真是亂啊。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，車爾尼先生站出來了。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站出來了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼先生一開始沒什麼名氣。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他發表了幾首曲子，但礙於感染者的身份，都是匿名發表的。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那幾首曲子也作得很好，甚至引來了高塔上的大人物，但他們一看車爾尼先生住在夕照區，都是扭頭就走。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到後來，他作了《晨暮》。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於《晨暮》的事，烏爾蘇拉大姐比我熟悉多了，讓她來講吧。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏爾蘇拉婆婆？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，其實也很簡單。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教先生鋼琴的老師有個女兒，和先生是好朋友。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個人的關係很好，水準又不相上下，相互都較著勁，都想著要壓過對方一頭。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，先生二十歲那年，那姑娘去世了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生受了好大的打擊，每天連話都不多說幾句，人也一天比一天瘦。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然有一天，他給我看一遝樂譜，說是自己作了新曲，這次無論如何也不想匿名發表了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時的伯爵大人——已經是現在這位女士了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知為什麼，伯爵大人找到了先生。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不僅當了先生的贊助人，還全力支持他的想法，上下打點，終於讓《晨暮》這首曲子署著車爾尼的名字，傳出了夕照區。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來還有這種事。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有點明白了，車爾尼先生所說的“意義”......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《晨暮》的反響實在太好，高塔上的大人物們這次實在不能視而不見，只能承認先生的才能。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，車爾尼先生就開始提攜夕照區內有音樂天賦的人了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這裡畢竟是萊塔尼亞，最不缺的就是音樂家！我自己是沒什麼天賦，但是......", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你謙虛啦。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前幾年你還一邊拉手風琴，一邊吆喝你的酸漬捲心菜呢。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，以前在工廠裡催大夥吃飯的時候，手風琴比吆喝聲好用多了。", "name": "小吃攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_494_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，在音樂徹底成為夕照區密不可分的一部分之後，危機總算是解除了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作曲、演奏、教學、樂器製造......", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好多人作的曲子還是匿名發表，大多數演奏家也出不了夕照區，但不管怎麼說，這些產業帶來的錢，終於讓夕照區站穩了腳跟。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在那之後不久，先生好像和伯爵大人大吵了一架。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大吵了一架？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是什麼理念的分歧......我也不懂那些東西。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然伯爵大人還是先生的贊助人，但從那以後，兩個人就很少來往了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行板？怎麼了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊的爺爺——不見了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我馬上回去！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slbellbtl", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您！再見！", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見，再見！有什麼不合身的地方儘管來找我，我幫你改！", "name": "裁縫店主"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（已經這麼晚了......黑鍵應該已經回家了吧。）", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_vibe_n"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，那是什麼......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石蟲？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}